    <tr><td><code>LanguageDialog()</code></td><td>Popup chon ngon ngu, luu vao localStorage.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>EditProfilePage()</code></td><td>Form sua profile: ho ten, email, sdt, ngay sinh, gioi tinh, avatar.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>HistoryPage()</code></td><td>Trang lich su xem. Hien lay API-only bang useApiVideoItems.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>ChangePasswordPage()</code></td><td>Form doi mat khau giao dien.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>FaqPage()</code></td><td>Danh sach cau hoi thuong gap.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>FeedbackPage()</code></td><td>Trang chon loai phan hoi.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>FeedbackFormPage()</code></td><td>Form nhap noi dung phan hoi, dem 1000 ky tu.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>VideoActionSheet()</code></td><td>Bottom sheet cho xoa/chia se phim.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>DeleteConfirmDialog()</code></td><td>Popup xac nhan xoa.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>VideoListPage()</code></td><td>Component dung chung cho Favorites va Followed.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>FavoritesPage()</code></td><td>Trang phim da thich, API-only.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>FollowedPage()</code></td><td>Trang phim da theo doi, API-only.</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h3>Luong Search</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Doc query tu URL: <code>/search?q=...</code>.</li>
    <li>Goi <code>useApiVideoItems()</code>.</li>
    <li>Loading: trang trong.</li>
    <li>API thanh cong: filter danh sach theo query.</li>
    <li>Nguoi dung search: cap nhat query, them chip, replace URL.</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Luong Profile</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Doc user tu <code>currentUser</code>.</li>
    <li>Doc profile tu <code>profileInfo</code>.</li>
    <li>Neu profile chua updated thi avatar trong va hien "chua cap nhat".</li>
    <li>Click sua profile di toi <code>/profile-edit</code>.</li>
    <li>Luu profile ghi lai <code>profileInfo</code> va cap nhat <code>currentUser</code>.</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Luong Language</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Mo <code>/profile-language</code>.</li>
    <li><code>LanguageDialog</code> lay ngon ngu hien tai tu localStorage.</li>
    <li>Chon ngon ngu va bam xac nhan.</li>
    <li>Luu <code>appLanguage</code>, quay ve profile.</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>10. Auth: LoginScreen.js</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Const / Function</th><th>Chuc nang</th></tr>
    <tr><td><code>authColors</code></td><td>Mau dung chung cho form auth.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>authInputSx(state)</code></td><td>Tra ve style MUI TextField theo trang thai default/focused/error.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>FieldLabel()</code></td><td>Label cho input.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>AuthInput()</code></td><td>Input dung chung cho login/register, co icon, helper text, state.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>AuthTabs()</code></td><td>Tab Dang nhap / Dang ky.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>SocialButton()</code></td><td>Nut Google/Facebook demo, hien alert chua ho tro.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>normalizeEmail(email)</code></td><td>Trim va lowercase email.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>getStoredUsers()</code></td><td>Doc user da dang ky trong localStorage.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>getAllUsers()</code></td><td>Gop user mau trong JSON va user localStorage.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>LoginScreen()</code></td><td>Form dang nhap, validate email/password, luu currentUser, chuyen sang /home.</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h3>Luong dang nhap</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Nguoi dung nhap email/password.</li>
    <li><code>handleChange</code> cap nhat state va xoa loi cua field do.</li>
    <li><code>handleSubmit</code> validate rong, validate email format.</li>
    <li>Tim account trong <code>getAllUsers()</code>.</li>
    <li>Neu dung mat khau: luu <code>currentUser</code> vao localStorage.</li>
    <li>Sau 500ms chuyen sang <code>/home</code>.</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>11. Auth: RegisterScreen.js</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Const / Function</th><th>Chuc nang</th></tr>
    <tr><td><code>emptyValues</code></td><td>Gia tri form dang ky rong.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>filledValues</code></td><td>Gia tri mau cho trang register-filled.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>errorMessages</code></td><td>Thong bao loi mac dinh.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>compactFieldSx</code></td><td>Style rut gon field register.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>compactSelectSx(state)</code></td><td>Style select gioi tinh.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>resetNewAccountState(user)</code></td><td>Reset profile/list cua user moi: profile chua cap nhat, watched/favorite/followed rong.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>genderState(value, error, focused)</code></td><td>Tinh trang thai select gioi tinh.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>RegisterScreen()</code></td><td>Form dang ky, validate, tao user moi va luu localStorage.</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h3>Luong dang ky</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Nguoi dung nhap thong tin.</li>
    <li><code>validate()</code> kiem tra ho ten, email, sdt, ngay sinh, gioi tinh, password.</li>
    <li>Kiem tra email da ton tai bang <code>getAllUsers()</code>.</li>
    <li>Tao <code>nextUser</code> voi <code>Date.now()</code> lam id.</li>
    <li>Luu vao <code>registeredUsers</code>.</li>
    <li>Luu <code>currentUser</code>.</li>
    <li>Goi <code>resetNewAccountState()</code>.</li>
    <li>Chuyen sang <code>/home</code>.</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>12. Layout Components</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>File</th><th>Function / Const</th><th>Chuc nang</th></tr>
    <tr><td><code>PhoneFrame.js</code></td><td><code>phoneSx</code></td><td>Style khung dien thoai: kich thuoc, nen, bong, responsive.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>PhoneFrame.js</code></td><td><code>PhoneFrame()</code></td><td>Boc noi dung vao khung phone.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>PageShell.js</code></td><td><code>PageShell()</code></td><td>Khung nen toan trang, can giua noi dung.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>EmptyStateScreen.js</code></td><td><code>orange</code></td><td>Mau cam dung cho illustration.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>EmptyStateScreen.js</code></td><td><code>Illustration(type)</code></td><td>Ve minh hoa bang Box va icon MUI.</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>EmptyStateScreen.js</code></td><td><code>EmptyStateScreen()</code></td><td>Man hinh thong bao nhu can dang nhap/mat ket noi.</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>13. Cac Page Wrapper Nho</h2>
  <p>Cac file nhu <code>LoginPage.js</code>, <code>LoginFilledPage.js</code>, <code>LoginErrorPage.js</code>, <code>RegisterPage.js</code>, <code>RegisterFilledPage.js</code>, <code>RegisterErrorPage.js</code>, <code>NoWifiPage.js</code>, <code>LoginRequiredPage.js</code> chu yeu la wrapper.</p>
  <p>Chuc nang cua chung: boc component chinh vao <code>PageShell</code> va truyen prop variant/type phu hop.</p>
  <p>Vi du:</p>
  <pre>function LoginPage() {
  return (
    &lt;PageShell&gt;
      &lt;LoginScreen /&gt;
    &lt;/PageShell&gt;
  );
}</pre>

  <h2>14. Vi Sao Dung API-only</h2>
  <p>Theo yeu cau hien tai, web khong duoc hien du lieu tinh cu khi mo trang. Dieu nay giup ban chung minh du lieu dang den tu API that.</p>
  <p>Cach lam:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>State ban dau de rong.</li>
    <li>Khong truyen fallback vao API service.</li>
    <li>Neu API loi thi throw error.</li>
    <li>UI loading la trang trong.</li>
    <li>UI error hien <code>Lỗi API</code>.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>So sanh voi fallback data: fallback giup app khong bi trong khi API loi, trai nghiem nguoi dung tot hon. Nhung fallback khien nguoi xem tuong rang web dang dung du lieu tinh. API-only phu hop khi can demo kha nang lay du lieu that.</p>

  <h2>15. Diem Can Biet Khi Duoc Hoi Ve Web</h2>
  <h3>Neu hoi: Web lay du lieu phim o dau?</h3>
  <p>Tra loi: Web lay du lieu tu AniList GraphQL API trong file <code>src/services/animeApi.js</code>. Trang home dung <code>fetchHomeAnime()</code>, cac trang phu dung <code>fetchAnimeCatalog()</code>.</p>

  <h3>Neu hoi: Web co dung backend rieng khong?</h3>
  <p>Tra loi: Chua co backend rieng. User va profile demo duoc luu bang localStorage; phim/anime lay tu API cong khai AniList.</p>

  <h3>Neu hoi: Vi sao luc mo trang bi trong?</h3>
  <p>Tra loi: Do web duoc cau hinh API-only. Trong luc cho API, web khong hien du lieu tinh de tranh nham lan. Khi API ve thi moi render danh sach.</p>

  <h3>Neu hoi: Neu API loi thi sao?</h3>
  <p>Tra loi: Service API se throw error, UI hien thong bao <code>Lỗi API</code>. Khong fallback sang du lieu cu.</p>

  <h3>Neu hoi: Dang nhap/dang ky that chua?</h3>
  <p>Tra loi: Dang nhap/dang ky hien la demo frontend. Tai khoan mau nam trong <code>users.json</code>, tai khoan dang ky moi luu localStorage.</p>

  <h3>Neu hoi: Profile luu o dau?</h3>
  <p>Tra loi: Profile luu trong localStorage voi key <code>profileInfo</code>.</p>

  <h3>Neu hoi: Doi ngon ngu hoat dong nhu nao?</h3>
  <p>Tra loi: Chon ngon ngu luu key <code>appLanguage</code> vao localStorage; Profile doc object text tu <code>languageText</code>.</p>

  <h2>16. Goi Y Nang Cap Sau Nay</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Dung <code>react-router-dom</code> thay cho routing thu cong.</li>
    <li>Dung React Query hoac SWR de quan ly API cache/loading/error chuyen nghiep hon.</li>
    <li>Tach <code>AnimeMockPages.js</code> thanh nhieu file nho: Profile, Search, Feedback, Lists.</li>
    <li>Lam backend that cho user/profile/favorite/history thay vi localStorage.</li>
    <li>Them API tin tuc that thay vi tao tin tu anime.</li>
    <li>Them skeleton loading neu muon trai nghiem tot hon, nhung hien tai ban dang yeu cau loading trong.</li>
    <li>Chuan hoa encoding tieng Viet trong mot so output terminal neu can review code dep hon.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>17. Tom Tat Ngan Gon</h2>
  <p>Du an HHTQ Anime la React SPA dung Vite va MUI. App vao <code>/login</code> dau tien, dang nhap/dang ky luu user bang localStorage, trang home va cac trang danh sach phim lay du lieu AniList API theo che do API-only. Hook quan trong nhat la <code>useApiVideoItems()</code>, service quan trong nhat la <code>animeApi.js</code>. UI duoc chia thanh component nhu PhoneFrame, PageShell, PosterTile, VideoRow, TopBar, BottomNav. Khi API thanh cong thi render phim; khi API loi thi bao loi; khi loading thi de trong.</p>
</body>
</html>
